{"tid":1257562,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)怪奇物語 第1-2季","createTime":"2019-06-25T15:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T17:40:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d72fa3eab14eeb13aa7f0653199d1a02edb2e394","tid":1257562,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=0e48a3c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=9877ee5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=f54cf5c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.horace.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/strangerthingsposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.horace.org%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fstrangerthingsposter.jpg&h=a330edad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mrbuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/stranger-things-2-e1509278997672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrbuzz.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fstranger-things-2-e1509278997672.jpg&h=82e7d808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事發生在1980年代，位於美國印第安納州的一座虛構城鎮霍金斯鎮（英語：Hawkins），鎮上的一座美國能源部名下的政府實驗室，涉及著跟超常現象跟超自然現象有關的機密實驗，當中還包含許多不為人知的人體實驗樣本。實驗人員在無意間開啟一條通往稱作「顛倒世界」（英語：Upside Down）的另一維度之傳送門，該維度所造成的危害隨著時間推及而波及到霍金斯鎮上的市民。<br />\n<br />\n第一季發生在1983年11月冬季，位於聖誕節期間，12歲男孩威爾&middot;拜爾斯被一隻來自於顛倒世界的神秘怪物擄走，他的離奇失蹤迫使親朋好友與當地警方不斷地搜查，一步一步捲入離奇的神秘事件中。隨著威爾的三個朋友私下調查，開始接觸到駭人的超自然力量。他們還碰上一名似乎來自實驗室的詭異小女孩，其受他們照顧之下自願跟著他們尋找失蹤的威爾，而實驗室隱藏的黑幕也被一個一個揭開。[8]<br />\n<br />\n第二季發生在1984年10月秋季，位於萬聖節期間，獲救的威爾經過一年調整，只有少數人知道一年前事故的真相。但由於威爾依然被一年前的陰影所影響，之後行為舉止開始變得詭異。威爾的親朋好友們開始想盡辦法幫助他時，得知他們生活的世界跟顛倒世界的抗爭並未結束，和平的表面下仍然隱藏著更大的威脅<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=eb99eeca\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=5da09477\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64729cce4566c692e40a3bca2f42371109604f2c","tid":1257562,"uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3